result: Last vacation was on the East Coast of Germany. It was generally a nice weekend, but we were only there for a few days before our flight to Paris and back. When we got there, it was a warm and sunny Sunday. I had no idea what was going on on the East Coast, and had no idea where we were going to be next.

In the next summer i will visit every festival in the country, to meet and listen to all the speakers and see all the artists and hear the stories.
The music will be fantastic
 I am looking forward to seeing a festival like this every year .
The festival will make me happy I am going to see the festival I am going to love it!!!!
This is the first year i will be attending this festival, and i have been planning on going to the festival since it first started.

Next summer i will be visiting the Southside Festival and try to catch up on all the music acts i missed because of covid.\nIt will be legendary! It kinda feels like doing it for the first time, it feels so weird to be close to people on such a huge scale, can' believe it will be possible again.

Hey Patrick, i wish you all the best for your birthday. i have a special gift for you. I hope we can see you around the block for your birthday this Saturday.\n\nThe letter was sent with love. love and gratitude to you.
